<s1>
<ptxt>
Check voltage using circuit tester and oscilloscope.
</ptxt>
<attention3>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Confirm that battery voltage is 11 V or more.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Outputs from terminals marked with (*) cannot be measured with voltmeter because they are pulse signals. Use oscilloscope for measuring these outputs.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</attention3>
